{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":478,"text":"Three and a half years ago,"},{"time":2213,"text":"I made one of the best decisions of my life."},{"time":5463,"text":"As my New Year's resolution,"},{"time":7526,"text":"I gave up dieting, stopped worrying about my weight,"},{"time":11765,"text":"and learned to eat mindfully."},{"time":14790,"text":"Now I eat whenever I'm hungry,"},{"time":18673,"text":"and I've lost 10 pounds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":21736,"text":"This was me at age 13,"},{"time":24273,"text":"when I started my first diet."},{"time":26813,"text":"I look at that picture now, and I think,"},{"time":29825,"text":"you did not need a diet,"},{"time":31659,"text":"you needed a fashion consult."},{"time":34330,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":36737,"text":"But I thought I needed to lose weight,"},{"time":39806,"text":"and when I gained it back,"},{"time":41268,"text":"of course I blamed myself."},{"time":45196,"text":"And for the next three decades,"},{"time":47703,"text":"I was on and off various diets."},{"time":50458,"text":"No matter what I tried,"},{"time":52530,"text":"the weight I'd lost always came back."},{"time":55361,"text":"I'm sure many of you know the feeling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58962,"text":"As a neuroscientist,"},{"time":60523,"text":"I wondered, why is this so hard?"},{"time":63337,"text":"Obviously, how much you weigh depends on"},{"time":65897,"text":"how much you eat and how much energy you burn."},{"time":68487,"text":"What most people don't realize"},{"time":70703,"text":"is that hunger and energy use"},{"time":72516,"text":"are controlled by the brain,"},{"time":74620,"text":"mostly without your awareness."},{"time":78135,"text":"Your brain does a lot of its work behind the scenes,"},{"time":81695,"text":"and that is a good thing,"},{"time":83911,"text":"because your conscious mind --"},{"time":86097,"text":"how do we put this politely? --"},{"time":87964,"text":"it's easily distracted."},{"time":91239,"text":"It's good that you don't have to remember to breathe"},{"time":93944,"text":"when you get caught up in a movie."},{"time":96584,"text":"You don't forget how to walk"},{"time":98601,"text":"because you're thinking about\nwhat to have for dinner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101516,"text":"Your brain also has its own sense"},{"time":103500,"text":"of what you should weigh,"},{"time":105265,"text":"no matter what you consciously believe."},{"time":108327,"text":"This is called your set point,"},{"time":110367,"text":"but that's a misleading term,"},{"time":112033,"text":"because it's actually a range"},{"time":113743,"text":"of about 10 or 15 pounds."},{"time":116307,"text":"You can use lifestyle choices to move your weight"},{"time":119530,"text":"up and down within that range,"},{"time":121598,"text":"but it's much, much harder to stay outside of it."},{"time":126003,"text":"The hypothalamus, the part of the brain"},{"time":128030,"text":"that regulates body weight,"},{"time":129943,"text":"there are more than a dozen chemical signals"},{"time":132366,"text":"in the brain that tell your body to gain weight,"},{"time":134982,"text":"more than another dozen that\ntell your body to lose it,"},{"time":138666,"text":"and the system works like a thermostat,"},{"time":141976,"text":"responding to signals from the body"},{"time":144323,"text":"by adjusting hunger, activity and metabolism,"},{"time":147931,"text":"to keep your weight stable as conditions change."},{"time":151657,"text":"That's what a thermostat does, right?"},{"time":153759,"text":"It keeps the temperature in your house the same"},{"time":157191,"text":"as the weather changes outside."},{"time":159951,"text":"Now you can try to change the temperature"},{"time":162773,"text":"in your house by opening a window in the winter,"},{"time":166269,"text":"but that's not going to change\nthe setting on the thermostat,"},{"time":170035,"text":"which will respond by kicking on the furnace"},{"time":172234,"text":"to warm the place back up."},{"time":174671,"text":"Your brain works exactly the same way,"},{"time":177993,"text":"responding to weight loss by using powerful tools"},{"time":181136,"text":"to push your body back"},{"time":182290,"text":"to what it considers normal."},{"time":186320,"text":"If you lose a lot of weight,"},{"time":188295,"text":"your brain reacts as if you were starving,"},{"time":192620,"text":"and whether you started out fat or thin,"},{"time":195252,"text":"your brain's response is exactly the same."},{"time":198217,"text":"We would love to think that your brain could tell"},{"time":200490,"text":"whether you need to lose weight or not,"},{"time":201956,"text":"but it can't."},{"time":204091,"text":"If you do lose a lot of weight,"},{"time":206984,"text":"you become hungry,"},{"time":209283,"text":"and your muscles burn less energy."},{"time":212169,"text":"Dr. Rudy Leibel of Columbia University"},{"time":214818,"text":"has found that people who have lost"},{"time":216527,"text":"10 percent of their body weight"},{"time":218726,"text":"burn 250 to 400 calories less"},{"time":221549,"text":"because their metabolism is suppressed."},{"time":224057,"text":"That's a lot of food."},{"time":226487,"text":"This means that a successful dieter"},{"time":228711,"text":"must eat this much less forever"},{"time":231879,"text":"than someone of the same weight"},{"time":233171,"text":"who has always been thin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235474,"text":"From an evolutionary perspective,"},{"time":237264,"text":"your body's resistance to weight loss makes sense."},{"time":239808,"text":"When food was scarce, our ancestors' survival"},{"time":242944,"text":"depended on conserving energy,"},{"time":245438,"text":"and regaining the weight when food was available"},{"time":247691,"text":"would have protected them\nagainst the next shortage."},{"time":250798,"text":"Over the course of human history,"},{"time":253325,"text":"starvation has been a much bigger problem"},{"time":256327,"text":"than overeating."},{"time":258011,"text":"This may explain a very sad fact:"},{"time":262242,"text":"Set points can go up,"},{"time":265071,"text":"but they rarely go down."},{"time":267943,"text":"Now, if your mother ever mentioned"},{"time":270132,"text":"that life is not fair,"},{"time":272428,"text":"this is the kind of thing she was talking about."},{"time":275221,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":278259,"text":"Successful dieting doesn't lower your set point."},{"time":281444,"text":"Even after you've kept the weight off"},{"time":282988,"text":"for as long as seven years,"},{"time":284817,"text":"your brain keeps trying to make you gain it back."},{"time":288790,"text":"If that weight loss had been due to a long famine,"},{"time":292080,"text":"that would be a sensible response."},{"time":294409,"text":"In our modern world of drive-thru burgers,"},{"time":297090,"text":"it's not working out so well for many of us."},{"time":300547,"text":"That difference between our ancestral past"},{"time":304290,"text":"and our abundant present"},{"time":306693,"text":"is the reason that Dr. Yoni Freedhoff"},{"time":308982,"text":"of the University of Ottawa"},{"time":311042,"text":"would like to take some of his patients back to a time"},{"time":313743,"text":"when food was less available,"},{"time":315842,"text":"and it's also the reason"},{"time":317543,"text":"that changing the food environment"},{"time":319927,"text":"is really going to be the most effective solution"},{"time":324043,"text":"to obesity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326153,"text":"Sadly, a temporary weight gain"},{"time":329430,"text":"can become permanent."},{"time":331475,"text":"If you stay at a high weight for too long,"},{"time":334109,"text":"probably a matter of years for most of us,"},{"time":336583,"text":"your brain may decide that that's the new normal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341021,"text":"Psychologists classify eaters into two groups,"},{"time":345081,"text":"those who rely on their hunger"},{"time":346699,"text":"and those who try to control their eating"},{"time":349268,"text":"through willpower, like most dieters."},{"time":355331,"text":"Let's call them intuitive eaters and controlled eaters."},{"time":361842,"text":"The interesting thing is that intuitive eaters"},{"time":364025,"text":"are less likely to be overweight,"},{"time":366656,"text":"and they spend less time thinking about food."},{"time":370358,"text":"Controlled eaters are more vulnerable"},{"time":374002,"text":"to overeating in response to advertising,"},{"time":376865,"text":"super-sizing, and the all-you-can-eat buffet."},{"time":380728,"text":"And a small indulgence,"},{"time":382473,"text":"like eating one scoop of ice cream,"},{"time":385679,"text":"is more likely to lead to a food binge"},{"time":391289,"text":"in controlled eaters."},{"time":393186,"text":"Children are especially vulnerable"},{"time":395113,"text":"to this cycle of dieting and then binging."},{"time":398242,"text":"Several long-term studies have shown"},{"time":401071,"text":"that girls who diet in their early teenage years"},{"time":405223,"text":"are three times more likely to become overweight"},{"time":408548,"text":"five years later,"},{"time":410085,"text":"even if they started at a normal weight,"},{"time":412904,"text":"and all of these studies found"},{"time":415553,"text":"that the same factors"},{"time":417860,"text":"that predicted weight gain"},{"time":421254,"text":"also predicted the development of eating disorders."},{"time":424254,"text":"The other factor, by the way,"},{"time":425822,"text":"those of you who are parents,"},{"time":427251,"text":"was being teased by family members"},{"time":430480,"text":"about their weight."},{"time":431991,"text":"So don't do that."},{"time":433827,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":435565,"text":"I left almost all my graphs at home,"},{"time":438201,"text":"but I couldn't resist throwing in just this one,"},{"time":440494,"text":"because I'm a geek, and that's how I roll."},{"time":442907,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":445386,"text":"This is a study that looked at the risk of death"},{"time":447734,"text":"over a 14-year period"},{"time":449600,"text":"based on four healthy habits:"},{"time":452102,"text":"eating enough fruits and vegetables,"},{"time":454222,"text":"exercise three times a week,"},{"time":456448,"text":"not smoking,"},{"time":457824,"text":"and drinking in moderation."},{"time":459794,"text":"Let's start by looking at the normal weight"},{"time":461723,"text":"people in the study."},{"time":463311,"text":"The height of the bars is the risk of death,"},{"time":465198,"text":"and those zero, one, two, three, four numbers"},{"time":467579,"text":"on the horizontal axis"},{"time":468825,"text":"are the number of those healthy habits"},{"time":470858,"text":"that a given person had."},{"time":472418,"text":"And as you'd expect, the healthier the lifestyle,"},{"time":475407,"text":"the less likely people were to die during the study."},{"time":478319,"text":"Now let's look at what happens"},{"time":479641,"text":"in overweight people."},{"time":481487,"text":"The ones that had no healthy habits"},{"time":483559,"text":"had a higher risk of death."},{"time":485330,"text":"Adding just one healthy habit"},{"time":487094,"text":"pulls overweight people back into the normal range."},{"time":490556,"text":"For obese people with no healthy habits,"},{"time":493298,"text":"the risk is very high, seven times higher"},{"time":496008,"text":"than the healthiest groups in the study."},{"time":498144,"text":"But a healthy lifestyle helps obese people too."},{"time":502084,"text":"In fact, if you look only at the group"},{"time":504602,"text":"with all four healthy habits,"},{"time":506876,"text":"you can see that weight makes very little difference."},{"time":509488,"text":"You can take control of your health"},{"time":511544,"text":"by taking control of your lifestyle,"},{"time":513418,"text":"even If you can't lose weight"},{"time":514899,"text":"and keep it off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":516635,"text":"Diets don't have very much reliability."},{"time":520745,"text":"Five years after a diet,"},{"time":522522,"text":"most people have regained the weight."},{"time":525310,"text":"Forty percent of them have gained even more."},{"time":527792,"text":"If you think about this,"},{"time":529217,"text":"the typical outcome of dieting"},{"time":531564,"text":"is that you're more likely to gain weight"},{"time":533452,"text":"in the long run than to lose it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":536221,"text":"If I've convinced you that dieting"},{"time":539075,"text":"might be a problem,"},{"time":541104,"text":"the next question is, what do you do about it?"},{"time":543742,"text":"And my answer, in a word, is mindfulness."},{"time":548198,"text":"I'm not saying you need to learn to meditate"},{"time":550733,"text":"or take up yoga."},{"time":552725,"text":"I'm talking about mindful eating:"},{"time":555277,"text":"learning to understand your body's signals"},{"time":558785,"text":"so that you eat when you're hungry"},{"time":561174,"text":"and stop when you're full,"},{"time":563516,"text":"because a lot of weight gain boils down"},{"time":565694,"text":"to eating when you're not hungry."},{"time":568760,"text":"How do you do it?"},{"time":570244,"text":"Give yourself permission to eat"},{"time":572078,"text":"as much as you want, and then work on figuring out"},{"time":574283,"text":"what makes your body feel good."},{"time":576035,"text":"Sit down to regular meals without distractions."},{"time":579764,"text":"Think about how your body feels"},{"time":581563,"text":"when you start to eat and when you stop,"},{"time":583617,"text":"and let your hunger decide"},{"time":586104,"text":"when you should be done."},{"time":587572,"text":"It took about a year for me to learn this,"},{"time":589993,"text":"but it's really been worth it."},{"time":591764,"text":"I am so much more relaxed around food"},{"time":594849,"text":"than I have ever been in my life."},{"time":597712,"text":"I often don't think about it."},{"time":600277,"text":"I forget we have chocolate in the house."},{"time":603010,"text":"It's like aliens have taken over my brain."},{"time":605954,"text":"It's just completely different."},{"time":608712,"text":"I should say that"},{"time":611378,"text":"this approach to eating probably\nwon't make you lose weight"},{"time":614171,"text":"unless you often eat when you're not hungry,"},{"time":617088,"text":"but doctors don't know of any approach"},{"time":620986,"text":"that makes significant weight loss in a lot of people,"},{"time":625461,"text":"and that is why a lot of people are now focusing on"},{"time":628831,"text":"preventing weight gain"},{"time":630990,"text":"instead of promoting weight loss."},{"time":634213,"text":"Let's face it:"},{"time":635749,"text":"If diets worked, we'd all be thin already."},{"time":639960,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":641860,"text":"Why do we keep doing the same thing"},{"time":643497,"text":"and expecting different results?"},{"time":646380,"text":"Diets may seem harmless,"},{"time":648063,"text":"but they actually do a lot of collateral damage."},{"time":651781,"text":"At worst, they ruin lives:"},{"time":654216,"text":"Weight obsession leads to eating disorders,"},{"time":656532,"text":"especially in young kids."},{"time":659475,"text":"In the U.S., we have 80 percent of 10-year-old girls"},{"time":664353,"text":"say they've been on a diet."},{"time":666130,"text":"Our daughters have learned to measure their worth"},{"time":668391,"text":"by the wrong scale."},{"time":671494,"text":"Even at its best,"},{"time":673519,"text":"dieting is a waste of time and energy."},{"time":676247,"text":"It takes willpower which you could be using"},{"time":680469,"text":"to help your kids with their homework"},{"time":683091,"text":"or to finish that important work project,"},{"time":686707,"text":"and because willpower is limited,"},{"time":690194,"text":"any strategy that relies on its consistent application"},{"time":694817,"text":"is pretty much guaranteed"},{"time":697600,"text":"to eventually fail you"},{"time":699693,"text":"when your attention moves on to something else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703542,"text":"Let me leave you with one last thought."},{"time":707474,"text":"What if we told all those dieting girls"},{"time":710377,"text":"that it's okay to eat when they're hungry?"},{"time":713378,"text":"What if we taught them to work with their appetite"},{"time":715628,"text":"instead of fearing it?"},{"time":717753,"text":"I think most of them would be happier and healthier,"},{"time":721180,"text":"and as adults,"},{"time":723195,"text":"many of them would probably be thinner."},{"time":726968,"text":"I wish someone had told me that"},{"time":729081,"text":"back when I was 13."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732502,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":734508,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}